---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="About Us | LT's Mobile Mechanics"
    description="Learn about LT's Mobile Mechanics, a locally owned, on-demand auto repair service based out of the Portland, Oregon area."
    canonical="https://ltsmobilemechanics.com/about/"
>
    <main>
        <section class="article-hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>About <em>LT's Mobile Mechanics</em></h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">
                    Honest, expert auto care that respects your time and your
                    vehicle.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="about-grid" style="align-items: start;">
                    <div class="about-content fade-up">
                        <p>
                            LT’s Mobile Mechanics is a locally owned, on-demand
                            auto repair service based out of the Portland,
                            Oregon area. We specialize in bringing professional,
                            reliable mechanic services directly to our
                            customers, whether they’re at home, work, or
                            stranded on the side of the road. We serve everyday
                            drivers, working families, and small business owners
                            who need fast, honest, and convenient vehicle
                            repairs without the hassle of a traditional shop.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            The business was founded to solve a real problem:
                            people don’t always have the time, tools, or ability
                            to get their vehicles into a shop, and too often
                            they’re hit with high prices, long wait times, or
                            unclear communication. LT’s Mobile Mechanics was
                            built to make car repair simpler, more transparent,
                            and more accessible.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            What really pushed me to start this business was
                            seeing how many people were stressed, overcharged,
                            or left without clear answers when it came to their
                            vehicles. I wanted to create something better,
                            something built on trust, skill, and convenience.
                            Before this, I was already working hands-on with
                            vehicles, building experience and seeing firsthand
                            what customers actually need and appreciate.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            At the core of LT’s Mobile Mechanics are strong
                            values. We don’t cut corners, we don’t upsell
                            unnecessary work, and we don’t leave customers in
                            the dark. Clear communication, fair pricing, and
                            quality work are non-negotiable. After working with
                            us, we want every customer to feel relieved,
                            confident in their vehicle, and respected throughout
                            the entire process.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="about-content fade-up"
                        style="transition-delay: 0.2s;"
                    >
                        <p>
                            What sets us apart is our convenience, honesty, and
                            hustle. We bring the shop to you, we explain things
                            in a way that makes sense, and we treat every
                            vehicle like it’s our own. We’re not just fixing
                            cars. We’re building relationships and earning trust
                            in the community.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            LT’s Mobile Mechanics is driven by skilled, hands-on
                            experience and a commitment to doing the job right.
                            Every repair is backed by real-world knowledge,
                            continuous learning, and a focus on staying
                            efficient and up to date with modern vehicles.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Looking ahead, the vision is to grow LT’s Mobile
                            Mechanics into a well-known and trusted name across
                            the Portland area and beyond. Expanding the team,
                            increasing service capacity, and continuing to raise
                            the standard for mobile auto repair. We also aim to
                            stay connected to the local community, helping
                            people when they need it most and providing
                            dependable service they can count on.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            So far, we’ve helped a wide range of customers
                            across many different types of repairs, from simple
                            maintenance like oil changes and brakes to more
                            complex jobs like starters, fuel systems, and
                            diagnostics. The results we’re most proud of are the
                            repeat customers, referrals, and the trust we’ve
                            built, because at the end of the day, that’s what
                            keeps this business moving forward.
                        </p>
                        <div style="margin-top: 32px;">
                            <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-gold"
                                >Contact Us Today</a
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
